I got this for my daughter as a Christmas present and to say she is a big fan is a understatement!!! I haven't watched this yet but looked at the back and I know she will love this. I will update this review with photos after she opens it.

***UPDATE**** 12/24
This is a very nice movie, but don't get if you are not a fan of the boys. You will LOVE this if you are as big of a fan as my daughter, she absolutely loved it.

This video is incredible! The live performances are amazing, full of energy, & emotion. I cried a lot. I love this band so much. I learned more about Michael, Calum, Luke, and Ashton. There were pics of them as kids and we got more info about their childhoods.
Incredible video. Definitely worth buying.

I loved this movie. It reflects how four normal lads from Sydney worked hard to get their dream come true, and their stories were amazing, their appreciation to their families, their hard work, their love to the fans, and when Michael got burned it broke my heart. This movie made me experiment a lot of feelings, like joy, pride, love, and many more. It's an amazing movie.
